➜太阳爆发大耀斑
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=24394	41040
NASA的太阳动力学观测卫星在6月7日探测到可能是近年来<a href="http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/sunearth/news/News060711-blast.html">最剧烈的太阳风暴爆发</a>（<a href="http://www.nasa.gov/multimedia/videogallery/index.html?collection_id=15504&amp;media_id=93779141">视频</a>）。<i>
